Dialogue: 0,00:21:50.35,00:21:51.90,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I’ll make it true
Dialogue: 0,00:21:51.93,00:21:54.08,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}my song 用魔法
Dialogue: 0,00:21:54.15,00:21:56.32,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}my days 谱写旋律
Dialogue: 0,00:21:56.35,00:22:00.79,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}回响在世界中
Dialogue: 0,00:22:00.98,00:22:03.17,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不断追赶着你
Dialogue: 0,00:22:03.17,00:22:05.34,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}直至引以自豪
Dialogue: 0,00:22:05.37,00:22:09.41,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我们都不会放弃
